com.tractrac.clientmodule
Class RaceCompetitor

java.lang.Object
  com.tractrac.clientmodule.details.Attachments
      com.tractrac.clientmodule.RaceCompetitor

public class RaceCompetitor
extends Attachments

Encapsulates data related to a specific Competitor of a specific Race.

An instance of this class is linked to a Competitor and a Race. Furthermore, it may be linked to a Route.

Custom data may be attached to each Race Competitor instance.

Use Race.getRaceCompetitor(com.tractrac.clientmodule.Competitor) to get the Race Competitor for a specific Competitor or Race.getRaceCompetitorList() to get a list of them all.
